# Google Sheets Configuration

# Method 1: Using JSON Credentials File (RECOMMENDED - Simpler, avoids key parsing issues)
# Place your service account JSON file in the project root (e.g., credentials.json)
# Then set the path to it:
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=./credentials.json

# Method 2: Using Environment Variables (Alternative)
# If you prefer not to use a JSON file, you can use these instead:
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_EMAIL=your-service-account-email@project-id.iam.gserviceaccount.com
# GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY=-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nYour private key here\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----

# Required: Google Sheet ID
GOOGLE_SHEET_ID=your-google-sheet-id-here

